{
  "video_id": "51k3UASQE5E",
  "title": "How whistle-blowers shape history | Kelly Richmond Pope",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13520.0,
      "end_time": 16296.0,
      "text": "How many of us have ever seen something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16320.0,
      "end_time": 18880.0,
      "text": "thought that we should report it, but decided not to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21120.0,
      "end_time": 23136.0,
      "text": "And not that I need to see a show of hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23160.0,
      "end_time": 26216.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m sure this has happened to someone in this room before."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26240.0,
      "end_time": 29415.0,
      "text": "In fact, when this question was asked to a group of employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29440.0,
      "end_time": 32936.0,
      "text": "46 percent of them responded by saying that they had seen something"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32960.0,
      "end_time": 34576.0,
      "text": "and decided not to report it."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34600.0,
      "end_time": 37736.0,
      "text": "So if you raised your hand, or quietly raised your hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37760.0,
      "end_time": 40560.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t feel bad, you&#39;re not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40800.0,
      "end_time": 43455.0,
      "text": "This message of if you see something to say something"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43480.0,
      "end_time": 45256.0,
      "text": "is really all around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45280.0,
      "end_time": 48976.0,
      "text": "Even when driving down the highway, you see billboards like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49000.0,
      "end_time": 52456.0,
      "text": "encouraging us to report crime without revealing ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52480.0,
      "end_time": 55215.0,
      "text": "But I still feel like a lot of us are really uncomfortable"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55240.0,
      "end_time": 57416.0,
      "text": "coming forward in the name of the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57440.0,
      "end_time": 60160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an accounting professor, and I do fraud research."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60400.0,
      "end_time": 64215.0,
      "text": "And in my class, I encourage my students to come forward with information"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 64239.00000000001,
      "end_time": 65455.00000000001,
      "text": "if they see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65480.00000000001,
      "end_time": 69216.0,
      "text": "Or in other words, encouraging my students to become whistle-blowers."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69240.0,
      "end_time": 72295.0,
      "text": "But if I&#39;m being completely honest with myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72320.0,
      "end_time": 75936.0,
      "text": "I am really conflicted with this message that I&#39;m sending to my students."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75960.0,
      "end_time": 77160.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s why."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78000.0,
      "end_time": 80800.0,
      "text": "Whistle-blowers are under attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81560.0,
      "end_time": 84760.0,
      "text": "Headline after headline shows us this."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 85960.0,
      "end_time": 88336.0,
      "text": "Many people choose not to become whistle-blowers"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88360.0,
      "end_time": 90616.0,
      "text": "due to the fear of retaliation."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90640.0,
      "end_time": 94336.0,
      "text": "From demotions to death threats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 94360.0,
      "end_time": 96256.0,
      "text": "to job loss --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96280.0,
      "end_time": 98136.0,
      "text": "perpetual job loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98160.0,
      "end_time": 101536.0,
      "text": "Choosing to become a whistle-blower is an uphill battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101560.0,
      "end_time": 103976.0,
      "text": "Their loyalty becomes into question."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104000.0,
      "end_time": 107216.0,
      "text": "Their motives, their trustworthiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107240.0,
      "end_time": 110976.0,
      "text": "So how can I, as a professor who really cares about her students"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111000.0,
      "end_time": 113960.0,
      "text": "encourage them to become whistle-blowers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113120.0,
      "end_time": 115680.0,
      "text": "when I know how the world truly feels about them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116720.0,
      "end_time": 119936.0,
      "text": "So, one day I was getting ready for my annual whistle-blower lecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 119960.0,
      "end_time": 121175.0,
      "text": "with my students."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121200.0,
      "end_time": 123336.0,
      "text": "And I was working on an article for \"Forbes,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 123360.0,
      "end_time": 125856.0,
      "text": "entitled \"Wells Fargo and Millennial Whistle-blowing."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125880.0,
      "end_time": 127950.0,
      "text": "What Do We Tell Them?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127120.0,
      "end_time": 130176.0,
      "text": "And as I was working on this piece and reading about the case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 130199.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131576.0,
      "text": "I became outraged."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 131600.0,
      "end_time": 135736.0,
      "text": "And what made me angry was when I came to the fact and realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 135760.0,
      "end_time": 138416.0,
      "text": "that the employees that tried to whistle-blow"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 138440.0,
      "end_time": 140136.0,
      "text": "were actually fired."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 140160.0,
      "end_time": 141496.0,
      "text": "And it really made me think"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 141520.0,
      "end_time": 144256.0,
      "text": "about the message that I was sharing with my students."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 144280.0,
      "end_time": 149960.0,
      "text": "And it made me think: What if my students had been Wells Fargo employees?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149120.0,
      "end_time": 153256.0,
      "text": "On the one hand, if they whistle-blew, they would have gotten fired."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153280.0,
      "end_time": 154616.0,
      "text": "But on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154640.0,
      "end_time": 157335.0,
      "text": "if they didn&#39;t report the frauds that they knew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 157360.0,
      "end_time": 159696.0,
      "text": "the way current regulation is written,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159720.0,
      "end_time": 162296.0,
      "text": "employees are held responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162320.0,
      "end_time": 164616.0,
      "text": "if they knew something and didn&#39;t report it."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164640.0,
      "end_time": 167616.0,
      "text": "So criminal prosecution is a real option."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167640.0,
      "end_time": 170815.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s a person supposed to do with those type of odds?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 170840.0,
      "end_time": 174776.0,
      "text": "I of all people know the valuable contributions"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174800.0,
      "end_time": 176336.0,
      "text": "that whistle-blowers make."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176360.0,
      "end_time": 179896.0,
      "text": "In fact, most frauds are discovered by them."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 179920.0,
      "end_time": 182856.0,
      "text": "Forty two percent of frauds are discovered by a whistle-blower"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182880.0,
      "end_time": 184736.0,
      "text": "in comparison to other methods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184760.0,
      "end_time": 187335.0,
      "text": "like measurement review and external audit."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 187360.0,
      "end_time": 189696.0,
      "text": "And when you think about some of the more classic"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189720.0,
      "end_time": 191336.0,
      "text": "or historical fraud cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191360.0,
      "end_time": 194960.0,
      "text": "it always is around a whistle-blower."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194120.0,
      "end_time": 196856.0,
      "text": "Think Watergate -- discovered by a whistle-blower."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196880.0,
      "end_time": 199775.0,
      "text": "Think Enron -- discovered by a whistle-blower."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 199800.0,
      "end_time": 204376.0,
      "text": "And who can forget about Bernard Madoff, discovered by a whistle-blower?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 204400.0,
      "end_time": 208856.0,
      "text": "It takes a tremendous amount of courage to come forward in the name of the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 208880.0,
      "end_time": 211576.0,
      "text": "But when we think about the term whistle-blower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 211600.0,
      "end_time": 215256.0,
      "text": "we often think of some very descriptive words:"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215280.0,
      "end_time": 216480.0,
      "text": "rat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217360.0,
      "end_time": 218560.0,
      "text": "snake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 219200.0,
      "end_time": 220816.0,
      "text": "traitor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 220840.0,
      "end_time": 223216.0,
      "text": "tattletale, weasel."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 223240.0,
      "end_time": 226816.0,
      "text": "And those are the nice words, the ones I can say from the stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 226840.0,
      "end_time": 228256.0,
      "text": "And so when I&#39;m not in class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 228280.0,
      "end_time": 231176.0,
      "text": "I go around the country and I interview white-collar felons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 231200.0,
      "end_time": 233215.0,
      "text": "whistle-blowers and victims of fraud."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 233240.0,
      "end_time": 236176.0,
      "text": "Because really I&#39;m trying to understand what makes them tick"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 236200.0,
      "end_time": 238799.0,
      "text": "and to bring those experiences back into the classroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 239680.0,
      "end_time": 243536.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s my interviews with whistle-blowers that really stick with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243560.0,
      "end_time": 244776.0,
      "text": "And they stick with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 244800.0,
      "end_time": 247960.0,
      "text": "because they make me question my own courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 247120.0,
      "end_time": 250976.0,
      "text": "When given the opportunity, would I actually speak up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 251000.0,
      "end_time": 253976.0,
      "text": "And so, this is a couple stories that I want to share with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 254000.0,
      "end_time": 255216.0,
      "text": "This is Mary."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 255240.0,
      "end_time": 258936.0,
      "text": "Mary Willingham is the whistle-blower from the University of North Carolina"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 258959.0,
      "end_time": 262135.0,
      "text": "at Chapel Hill, academic fraud case."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 262160.0,
      "end_time": 265616.0,
      "text": "And Mary was a learning specialist at the university,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 265640.0,
      "end_time": 268656.0,
      "text": "and she worked with students, primarily student athletes."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 268680.0,
      "end_time": 271375.0,
      "text": "And what she noticed, when she was working with students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 271399.0,
      "end_time": 274136.0,
      "text": "is they were turning in term papers"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 274160.0,
      "end_time": 277256.0,
      "text": "that seemed well beyond their reading levels."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 277280.0,
      "end_time": 279215.0,
      "text": "She started to ask a couple of questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 279240.0,
      "end_time": 281256.0,
      "text": "and she found out that there was a database"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 281280.0,
      "end_time": 284655.0,
      "text": "where the student athletes could retrieve papers and turn them in."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 284680.0,
      "end_time": 287136.0,
      "text": "And then she found out that some of her colleagues"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 287160.0,
      "end_time": 293376.0,
      "text": "were funneling students into fake classes, just to keep them eligible to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 293400.0,
      "end_time": 296135.0,
      "text": "Now, when Mary found this out, she was outraged."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 296160.0,
      "end_time": 299960.0,
      "text": "And so what she tried to do was go to her direct supervisor."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 299120.0,
      "end_time": 300976.0,
      "text": "But they didn&#39;t do anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 301000.0,
      "end_time": 304816.0,
      "text": "And then Mary tried to go to some internal university administrators."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 304840.0,
      "end_time": 306455.0,
      "text": "And they didn&#39;t do anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 306480.0,
      "end_time": 308856.0,
      "text": "So, what happens when nobody listens?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 308880.0,
      "end_time": 310960.0,
      "text": "You blog."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 310120.0,
      "end_time": 311976.0,
      "text": "So Mary decided to develop a blog."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 312000.0,
      "end_time": 314656.0,
      "text": "Her blog went viral within 24 hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 314680.0,
      "end_time": 317176.0,
      "text": "and she was contacted by a reporter."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 317200.0,
      "end_time": 319496.0,
      "text": "Now, when she was contacted by this reporter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 319520.0,
      "end_time": 321296.0,
      "text": "her identity was known."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 321320.0,
      "end_time": 322656.0,
      "text": "She was exposed."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 322680.0,
      "end_time": 326496.0,
      "text": "And when she was exposed, she received a demotion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 326520.0,
      "end_time": 329560.0,
      "text": "death threats, over collegiate sports."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 330280.0,
      "end_time": 334950.0,
      "text": "Mary didn&#39;t do anything wrong. She didn&#39;t participate in the fraud."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 334120.0,
      "end_time": 336336.0,
      "text": "She really thought that she was giving voice"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 336360.0,
      "end_time": 338656.0,
      "text": "to students that were voiceless."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 338680.0,
      "end_time": 341560.0,
      "text": "But her loyalty was questioned."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 341800.0,
      "end_time": 343719.0,
      "text": "Her trustworthiness and her motives."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 345480.0,
      "end_time": 348856.0,
      "text": "Now, whistle-blowing doesn&#39;t always have to end"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 348880.0,
      "end_time": 350576.0,
      "text": "in demotions or death threats."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 350600.0,
      "end_time": 354536.0,
      "text": "Actually, in 2002, this was the cover of \"Time\" magazine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 354560.0,
      "end_time": 357896.0,
      "text": "where we were actually honoring three brave whistle-blowers"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 357920.0,
      "end_time": 360856.0,
      "text": "for their decision to come forward in the name of the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 360880.0,
      "end_time": 362536.0,
      "text": "And when you look at the research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 362560.0,
      "end_time": 366136.0,
      "text": "22 percent of whistle-blowers actually report retaliation."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 366160.0,
      "end_time": 371616.0,
      "text": "So there is a huge population of people that report and are not retaliated against"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 371640.0,
      "end_time": 373159.0,
      "text": "and that gives me hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 374280.0,
      "end_time": 375936.0,
      "text": "So this is Kathe."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 375960.0,
      "end_time": 380376.0,
      "text": "Kathe Swanson is a retired city clerk from the city of Dixon."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 380400.0,
      "end_time": 384560.0,
      "text": "And one day, Kathe was doing her job, just like she always did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 384800.0,
      "end_time": 387816.0,
      "text": "and she stumbled upon a pretty interesting case."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 387840.0,
      "end_time": 389695.0,
      "text": "See, Kathe was at the end of the month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 389720.0,
      "end_time": 392496.0,
      "text": "and she was doing her treasures report for the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 392520.0,
      "end_time": 396575.0,
      "text": "and typically, her boss, Rita Crundwell, gave her a list of accounts and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 396600.0,
      "end_time": 399576.0,
      "text": "\"Kathe, call the bank and get these specific accounts.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 399600.0,
      "end_time": 401256.0,
      "text": "And Kathe did her job."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 401280.0,
      "end_time": 402655.0,
      "text": "But this particular day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 402680.0,
      "end_time": 405136.0,
      "text": "Rita was out of town, and Kathe was busy."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 405160.0,
      "end_time": 410336.0,
      "text": "She picks up the phone, she calls the bank and says, \"Fax me all of the accounts.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 410360.0,
      "end_time": 413656.0,
      "text": "And when she gets the fax, she sees that there is an account"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 413680.0,
      "end_time": 415816.0,
      "text": "that has some withdrawals and deposits in it"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 415840.0,
      "end_time": 417296.0,
      "text": "that she did not know about."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 417320.0,
      "end_time": 420616.0,
      "text": "It was an account controlled only by Rita."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 420640.0,
      "end_time": 424616.0,
      "text": "So Kathe looked at the information, she reported it to her direct supervisor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 424640.0,
      "end_time": 426776.0,
      "text": "which was then-mayor Burke,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 426800.0,
      "end_time": 430560.0,
      "text": "and this led into a huge investigation, a six-month investigation."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 431200.0,
      "end_time": 436216.0,
      "text": "Come to find out, Kathe&#39;s boss, Rita Crundwell, was embezzling money."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 436240.0,
      "end_time": 441456.0,
      "text": "Rita was embezzling 53 million dollars over a 20-year period,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 441480.0,
      "end_time": 443960.0,
      "text": "and Kathe just happened to stumble upon it."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 445800.0,
      "end_time": 448150.0,
      "text": "Kathe is a hero."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 448400.0,
      "end_time": 449736.0,
      "text": "And actually, I had the opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 449760.0,
      "end_time": 453135.0,
      "text": "of interviewing Kathe for my documentary, \"All the Queen&#39;s Horses.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 453160.0,
      "end_time": 455496.0,
      "text": "And Kathe wasn&#39;t seeking fame."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 455520.0,
      "end_time": 458976.0,
      "text": "In fact, she really didn&#39;t want to talk to me for a really long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 459000.0,
      "end_time": 462960.0,
      "text": "but through strategic stalking, she ended up doing the interview."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 462120.0,
      "end_time": 463256.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 463280.0,
      "end_time": 465496.0,
      "text": "But she was seeking fairness, not fame."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 465520.0,
      "end_time": 467135.0,
      "text": "And if it wasn&#39;t for Kathe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 467160.0,
      "end_time": 469800.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s to say this fraud would have ever been discovered?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 471120.0,
      "end_time": 473736.0,
      "text": "So, remember that \"Forbes\" article I was talking about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 473760.0,
      "end_time": 475664.0,
      "text": "that I was working on before my lecture?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 475689.0,
      "end_time": 479256.0,
      "text": "Well, I posted it and something really fantastic happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 479280.0,
      "end_time": 483976.0,
      "text": "I started receiving emails from whistle-blowers all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 484000.0,
      "end_time": 487576.0,
      "text": "And as I was receiving these emails and responding back to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 487600.0,
      "end_time": 490256.0,
      "text": "there was a common theme in the message that I received,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 490280.0,
      "end_time": 491496.0,
      "text": "and this is what it was:"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 491520.0,
      "end_time": 495895.0,
      "text": "they all said this, \"I blew the whistle, people really hate me now."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 495920.0,
      "end_time": 498960.0,
      "text": "I got fired, but guess what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 498120.0,
      "end_time": 501496.0,
      "text": "I would do it all over again if I could.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 501520.0,
      "end_time": 504736.0,
      "text": "And so as I kept reading this message, all these messages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 504760.0,
      "end_time": 507575.0,
      "text": "I wanted to think, what could I share with my students?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 507600.0,
      "end_time": 511176.0,
      "text": "And so, I pulled it all together and this is what I learned."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 511200.0,
      "end_time": 514295.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s important for us to cultivate hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 514320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516256.00000000006,
      "text": "Whistle-blowers are hopeful."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 516280.0,
      "end_time": 517696.0,
      "text": "Despite popular belief,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 517720.0,
      "end_time": 522160.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not all disgruntled employees that have a beef with the company."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 522390.0,
      "end_time": 526216.0,
      "text": "Their hopefulness really is what drives them to come forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 526240.0,
      "end_time": 528655.0,
      "text": "We also have to cultivate commitment."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 528679.0,
      "end_time": 530535.0,
      "text": "Whistle-blowers are committed."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 530559.0,
      "end_time": 533550.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s that passion to their organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 533800.0,
      "end_time": 535496.0,
      "text": "that makes them want to come forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 535520.0,
      "end_time": 537136.0,
      "text": "Whistle-blowers are humble."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 537160.0,
      "end_time": 541216.0,
      "text": "Again, they&#39;re not seeking fame, but they are seeking fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 541240.0,
      "end_time": 544960.0,
      "text": "And we need to continue to cultivate bravery."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 544120.0,
      "end_time": 545696.0,
      "text": "Whistle-blowers are brave."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 545720.0,
      "end_time": 549416.0,
      "text": "Often, they underestimated"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 549440.0,
      "end_time": 552560.0,
      "text": "the impact whistle-blowing had on their family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 552800.0,
      "end_time": 557000.0,
      "text": "but what they continue to comment on is how hard it is to withhold the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 557960.0,
      "end_time": 560776.0,
      "text": "With that, I want to leave you with one additional name:"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 560800.0,
      "end_time": 562120.0,
      "text": "Peter Buxtun."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 563160.0,
      "end_time": 569336.0,
      "text": "Peter Buxtun was a 27-year-old employee for the US Public Health Service."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 569360.0,
      "end_time": 573296.0,
      "text": "And he was hired to interview people"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 573320.0,
      "end_time": 575696.0,
      "text": "that had sexually transmitted diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 575720.0,
      "end_time": 577776.0,
      "text": "And through the course of his work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 577800.0,
      "end_time": 581736.0,
      "text": "he noticed a clinical study that was going on within the organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 581760.0,
      "end_time": 585856.0,
      "text": "And it was a study that was looking at the progression of untreated syphilis."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 585880.0,
      "end_time": 588656.0,
      "text": "And so, there were 600 African American males"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 588680.0,
      "end_time": 589896.0,
      "text": "that were in this study."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 589920.0,
      "end_time": 591496.0,
      "text": "They were enticed into the study"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 591520.0,
      "end_time": 595456.0,
      "text": "through being given free medical exams, burial insurance."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 595480.0,
      "end_time": 599176.0,
      "text": "And so, what happened through the course of this study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 599200.0,
      "end_time": 604960.0,
      "text": "is penicillin was discovered to help treat syphilis."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 604120.0,
      "end_time": 606560.0,
      "text": "And what Peter noticed was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 606800.0,
      "end_time": 610160.0,
      "text": "the participants in this study were not given the penicillin"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 610400.0,
      "end_time": 611536.0,
      "text": "to treat their syphilis."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 611560.0,
      "end_time": 613376.0,
      "text": "And the participants didn&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 613400.0,
      "end_time": 618576.0,
      "text": "So similar to Mary, Peter tried to report and talk to his internal supervisors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 618600.0,
      "end_time": 620336.0,
      "text": "but no one listened."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 620360.0,
      "end_time": 622776.0,
      "text": "And so Peter thought this was completely unfair"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 622800.0,
      "end_time": 624376.0,
      "text": "and he tried to report again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 624400.0,
      "end_time": 628550.0,
      "text": "and finally talked to a reporter -- very similar to Mary."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 628800.0,
      "end_time": 632376.0,
      "text": "And in 1972, this was the front page of the \"New York Times\":"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 632400.0,
      "end_time": 636480.0,
      "text": "\"Syphilis Victims in US Study Went Untreated for 40 Years.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 637640.0,
      "end_time": 642560.0,
      "text": "This is known to us today as the Tuskegee syphilis experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 642800.0,
      "end_time": 644296.0,
      "text": "And Peter was the whistle-blower."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 644320.0,
      "end_time": 648376.0,
      "text": "What happened to the 600 men, you may wonder, the 600 original men?"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 648400.0,
      "end_time": 651376.0,
      "text": "Twenty eight men died from syphilis."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 651400.0,
      "end_time": 654536.0,
      "text": "One hundred died from syphilis complications,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 654560.0,
      "end_time": 656415.0,
      "text": "forty wives were infected"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 656440.0,
      "end_time": 659296.0,
      "text": "and 10 children were born with congenital syphilis."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 659320.0,
      "end_time": 661656.0,
      "text": "Who&#39;s to say what these numbers would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 661680.0,
      "end_time": 665776.0,
      "text": "if it wasn&#39;t for the brave, courageous act of Peter?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 665800.0,
      "end_time": 668295.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all connected to Peter, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 668320.0,
      "end_time": 670896.0,
      "text": "If you know anybody that&#39;s in a clinical trial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 670920.0,
      "end_time": 674960.0,
      "text": "the reason why we have informed consent today"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 674120.0,
      "end_time": 676240.0,
      "text": "is because of Peter&#39;s courageous act."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 677400.0,
      "end_time": 678816.0,
      "text": "So let me ask you a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 678840.0,
      "end_time": 681736.0,
      "text": "That original question, a variation of the original question."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 681760.0,
      "end_time": 684856.0,
      "text": "How many of us have ever used the term"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 684880.0,
      "end_time": 687856.0,
      "text": "snitch, rat"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 687880.0,
      "end_time": 689456.0,
      "text": "tattletale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 689480.0,
      "end_time": 691136.0,
      "text": "snake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 691160.0,
      "end_time": 692656.0,
      "text": "weasel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 692680.0,
      "end_time": 693880.0,
      "text": "leak?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 694920.0,
      "end_time": 696120.0,
      "text": "Anybody?"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 699640.0,
      "end_time": 702696.0,
      "text": "Before you get the urge to do that again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 702720.0,
      "end_time": 704536.0,
      "text": "I want you to think a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 704560.0,
      "end_time": 708439.0,
      "text": "It might be the Mary, the Peter, the Kathes of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 709480.0,
      "end_time": 712416.0,
      "text": "You might be the person that could shape history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 712440.0,
      "end_time": 714976.0,
      "text": "or they could be the person that shapes yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 715000.0,
      "end_time": 716216.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 716240.0,
      "end_time": 720000.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}